{"type":"message","id":"52008f08","parentId":"7427158a","timestamp":"2026-03-22T14:43:00.641Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool_X6D4pjtG6W2j1ygh3MP70qfS","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"API Key: sk-kimi-Y311pdLbY8kXigdqhyjfKBjhNdzl4WRzJFderDmHC8eLPhwJMrTmSuG5e8jeaqND\nAuth Token: sk-kimi-Y311pdLbY8kXigdqhyjfKBjhNdzl4WRzJFderDmHC8eLPhwJMrTmSuG5e8jeaqND\n{\n  \"error\": \"Invalid auth token\"\n}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1084,"aggregated":"API Key: sk-kimi-Y311pdLbY8kXigdqhyjfKBjhNdzl4WRzJFderDmHC8eLPhwJMrTmSuG5e8jeaqND\nAuth Token: sk-kimi-Y311pdLbY8kXigdqhyjfKBjhNdzl4WRzJFderDmHC8eLPhwJMrTmSuG5e8jeaqND\n{\n  \"error\": \"Invalid auth token\"\n}","cwd":"/home/hochoy/.openclaw/workspace-demo"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774190580639}}
{"type":"message","id":"d0123ebe","parentId":"52008f08","timestamp":"2026-03-22T14:43:07.011Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"这个key不适用于desearch.ai服务。让我尝试用agent-reach技能来搜索。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_hGYttgNeSgmjlyOlt30fTlL4","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"~/.openclaw/skills/agent-reach/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":378,"output":48,"cacheRead":16896,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17322,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774190580642}}
{"type":"message","id":"4f6b786e","parentId":"d0123ebe","timestamp":"2026-03-22T14:43:07.016Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool_hGYttgNeSgmjlyOlt30fTlL4","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: agent-reach\ndescription: >\n  Give your AI agent eyes to see the entire internet. 7500+ GitHub stars.\n  Search and read 14 platforms: Twitter/X, Reddit, YouTube, GitHub, Bilibili,\n  XiaoHongShu (小红书), Douyin (抖音), Weibo (微博), WeChat Articles (微信公众号),\n  LinkedIn, Instagram, RSS, Exa web search, and any web page.\n  One command install, zero config for 8 channels, agent-reach doctor for diagnostics.\n  Use when: (1) user asks to search or read any of these platforms,\n  (2) user shares a URL from any supported platform,\n  (3) user asks to search the web, find information online, or research a topic,\n  (4) user asks to post, comment, or interact on supported platforms,\n  (5) user asks to configure or set up a platform channel.\n  Triggers: \"搜推特\", \"搜小红书\", \"看视频\", \"搜一下\", \"上网搜\", \"帮我查\", \"全网搜索\",\n  \"search twitter\", \"read tweet\", \"youtube transcript\", \"search reddit\",\n  \"read this link\", \"看这个链接\", \"B站\", \"bilibili\", \"抖音视频\",\n  \"微信文章\", \"公众号\", \"LinkedIn\", \"GitHub issue\", \"RSS\", \"微博\",\n  \"search online\", \"web search\", \"find information\", \"research\",\n  \"帮我配\", \"configure twitter\", \"configure proxy\", \"帮我安装\".\nmetadata:\n  openclaw:\n    homepage: https://github.com/Panniantong/Agent-Reach\n---\n\n# Agent Reach — Usage Guide\n\nUpstream tools for 13+ platforms. Call them directly.\n\nRun `agent-reach doctor` to check which channels are available.\n\n## ⚠️ Workspace Rules\n\n**Never create files in the agent workspace.** Use `/tmp/` for temporary output and `~/.agent-reach/` for persistent data.\n\n## Web — Any URL\n\n```bash\ncurl -s \"https://r.jina.ai/URL\"\n```\n\n## Web Search (Exa)\n\n```bash\nmcporter call 'exa.web_search_exa(query: \"query\", numResults: 5)'\nmcporter call 'exa.get_code_context_exa(query: \"code question\", tokensNum: 3000)'\n```\n\n## Twitter/X (xreach)\n\n```bash\nxreach search \"query\" -n 10 --json          # search\nxreach tweet URL_OR_ID --json                # read tweet (supports /status/ and /article/ URLs)\nxreach tweets @username -n 20 --json         # user timeline\nxreach thread URL_OR_ID --json               # full thread\n```\n\n## YouTube (yt-dlp)\n\n```bash\nyt-dlp --dump-json \"URL\"                     # video metadata\nyt-dlp --write-sub --write-auto-sub --sub-lang \"zh-Hans,zh,en\" --skip-download -o \"/tmp/%(id)s\" \"URL\"\n                                             # download subtitles, then read the .vtt file\nyt-dlp --dump-json \"ytsearch5:query\"         # search\n```\n\n## Bilibili (yt-dlp)\n\n```bash\nyt-dlp --dump-json \"https://www.bilibili.com/video/BVxxx\"\nyt-dlp --write-sub --write-auto-sub --sub-lang \"zh-Hans,zh,en\" --convert-subs vtt --skip-download -o \"/tmp/%(id)s\" \"URL\"\n```\n\n> Server IPs may get 412. Use `--cookies-from-browser chrome` or configure proxy.\n\n## Reddit\n\n```bash\ncurl -s \"https://www.reddit.com/r/SUBREDDIT/hot.json?limit=10\" -H \"User-Agent: agent-reach/1.0\"\ncurl -s \"https://www.reddit.com/search.json?q=QUERY&limit=10\" -H \"User-Agent: agent-reach/1.0\"\n```\n\n> Server IPs may get 403. Search via Exa instead, or configure proxy.\n\n## GitHub (gh CLI)\n\n```bash\ngh search repos \"query\" --sort stars --limit 10\ngh repo view owner/repo\ngh search code \"query\" --language python\ngh issue list -R owner/repo --state open\ngh issue view 123 -R owner/repo\n```\n\n## 小红书 / XiaoHongShu (mcporter)\n\n```bash\nmcporter call 'xiaohongshu.search_feeds(keyword: \"query\")'\nmcporter call 'xiaohongshu.get_feed_detail(feed_id: \"xxx\", xsec_token: \"yyy\")'\nmcporter call 'xiaohongshu.get_feed_detail(feed_id: \"xxx\", xsec_token: \"yyy\", load_all_comments: true)'\nmcporter call 'xiaohongshu.publish_content(title: \"标题\", content: \"正文\", images: [\"/path/img.jpg\"], tags: [\"tag\"])'\n```\n\n> Requires login. Use Cookie-Editor to import cookies.\n\n## 抖音 / Douyin (mcporter)\n\n```bash\nmcporter call 'douyin.parse_douyin_video_info(share_link: \"https://v.douyin.com/xxx/\")'\nmcporter call 'douyin.get_douyin_download_link(share_link: \"https://v.douyin.com/xxx/\")'\n```\n\n> No login needed.\n\n## 微信公众号 / WeChat Articles\n\n**Search** (miku_ai):\n```python\npython3 -c \"\nimport asyncio\nfrom miku_ai import get_wexin_article\nasync def s():\n    for a in await get_wexin_article('query', 5):\n        print(f'{a[\\\"title\\\"]} | {a[\\\"url\\\"]}')\nasyncio.run(s())\n\"\n```\n\n**Read** (Camoufox — bypasses WeChat anti-bot):\n```bash\ncd ~/.agent-reach/tools/wechat-article-for-ai && python3 main.py \"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/ARTICLE_ID\"\n```\n\n> WeChat articles cannot be read with Jina Reader or curl. Must use Camoufox.\n\n## LinkedIn (mcporter)\n\n```bash\nmcporter call 'linkedin.get_person_profile(linkedin_url: \"https://linkedin.com/in/username\")'\nmcporter call 'linkedin.search_people(keyword: \"AI engineer\", limit: 10)'\n```\n\nFallback: `curl -s \"https://r.jina.ai/https://linkedin.com/in/username\"`\n\n## RSS (feedparser)\n\n## RSS\n\n```python\npython3 -c \"\nimport feedparser\nfor e in feedparser.parse('FEED_URL').entries[:5]:\n    print(f'{e.title} — {e.link}')\n\"\n```\n\n## Troubleshooting\n\n- **Channel not working?** Run `agent-reach doctor` — shows status and fix instructions.\n- **Twitter fetch failed?** Ensure `undici` is installed: `npm install -g undici`. Configure proxy: `agent-reach configure proxy URL`.\n\n## Setting Up a Channel (\"帮我配 XXX\")\n\nIf a channel needs setup (cookies, Docker, etc.), fetch the install guide:\nhttps://raw.githubusercontent.com/Panniantong/agent-reach/main/docs/install.md\n\nUser only provides cookies. Everything else is your job.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774190587015}}
{"type":"message","id":"48292305","parentId":"4f6b786e","timestamp":"2026-03-22T14:43:14.545Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"很好，我可以使用 agent-reach 中的 `curl -s \"https://r.jina.ai/URL\"` 来抓取网页内容。让我试试用这个来获取toolify.ai的内容。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_s5VFyi5qPGUlhEcuu5EKlny7","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s \"https://r.jina.ai/https://www.toolify.ai/zh/\" --max-time 30"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":1704,"output":77,"cacheRead":17152,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":18933,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774190587017}}
{"type":"message","id":"e9f77b7d","parentId":"48292305","timestamp":"2026-03-22T14:43:16.140Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool_s5VFyi5qPGUlhEcuu5EKlny7","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"API Key: sk-kimi-Y311pdLbY8kXigdqhyjfKBjhNdzl4WRzJFderDmHC8eLPhwJMrTmSuG5e8jeaqND\nAuth Token: sk-kimi-Y311pdLbY8kXigdqhyjfKBjhNdzl4WRzJFderDmHC8eLPhwJMrTmSuG5e8jeaqND\nTitle: 最好的AI导航站和AI工具列表 - Toolify\n\nURL Source: https://www.toolify.ai/zh/\n\nMarkdown Content:\n# 最好的AI导航站和AI工具列表 - Toolify\n\nSponsored by ThumbnailCreator.com -AI工具，用于快速创建令人惊艳的YouTube缩略图。\n\n[Toolify![Image 1: Toolify logo](https://www.toolify.ai/3.3.2/img/logo.f3a91ce.png)](https://www.toolify.ai/zh/)\n\n[免费工具](https://www.toolify.ai/zh/free-ai-tools)\n\n[AI产品](https://www.toolify.ai/zh/)\n\n*   [最新推出 最新上架的AI，每日更新](https://www.toolify.ai/zh/new)\n*   [最多保存 获得最多收藏的AI工具](https://www.toolify.ai/zh/most-saved)\n*   [流量最高 网站流量最高的AI工具](https://www.toolify.ai/zh/most-used)\n*   [AI Apps 按App分类的AI工具](https://www.toolify.ai/zh/apps)\n*   [Discord of AI AI的Discord社区](https://www.toolify.ai/zh/discord)\n*   [AI 谷歌插件 按浏览器插件分类的AI工具](https://www.toolify.ai/zh/browser-extension)\n*   [GPTs 来自GPT Store 的GPTs](https://www.toolify.ai/zh/gpts)\n*   [AI模型 发现最佳AI模型](https://www.toolify.ai/zh/ai-model)\n\n[分类](https://www.toolify.ai/zh/category)\n\n[排行榜](https://www.toolify.ai/zh/Best-trending-AI-Tools)\n\n*   [AI月榜 依据月份和月访问量划分的AI网站榜单](https://www.toolify.ai/zh/Best-trending-AI-Tools)\n*   [AI分类榜 依据分类和月访问量划分的AI网站榜单](https://www.toolify.ai/zh/Best-AI-Tools-Category)\n*   [AI地区榜 依据地区和月访问量划分的AI网站榜单](https://www.toolify.ai/zh/Best-AI-Tools-region)\n*   [AI渠道榜 依据来源和月访问量划分的AI网站榜单](https://www.toolify.ai/zh/Best-AI-Tools-Source)\n*   [AI收入榜 依据支付排名和实际流量的AI高收入榜](https://www.toolify.ai/zh/Best-AI-Tools-revenue)\n\n[提示词](https://www.toolify.ai/zh/n8n)\n\n*   [n8n 工作流](https://www.toolify.ai/zh/n8n)\n*   [Midjourney 提示词](https://www.toolify.ai/zh/midjourney-library)\n*   [Openclaw 技能](https://www.toolify.ai/zh/openclaw-skills)\n\n[职业](https://www.toolify.ai/jobs)\n\n[研究](https://www.toolify.ai/zh/profile/insights)\n\n*   [网站洞察](https://www.toolify.ai/zh/profile/insights)\n*   [社媒聆听](https://www.toolify.ai/zh/social-listening)\n*   [研究报告](https://www.toolify.ai/zh/research-report)\n\n[提交](https://www.toolify.ai/zh/submit)\n\n*   [提交](https://www.toolify.ai/zh/submit)\n*   [广告](https://www.toolify.ai/zh/advertise)\n*   [Guest Posts / Link Insert](https://www.toolify.ai/zh/post-or-insert)\n*   [更新AI](https://www.toolify.ai/zh/update-ai)\n*   [提交GPT](https://www.toolify.ai/zh/submit-gpt)\n*   [更多业务](https://www.toolify.ai/zh/business)\n\nAI 广告资料库\n\n[登录](https://www.toolify.ai/zh/login)\n\n zh\n\nSponsored by i10X\n\n# 发现最好的 AI网站和AI工具\n\n[28481 个AI工具和](https://www.toolify.ai/zh/)[459 个分类](https://www.toolify.ai/zh/category) 已收录于最大的AI工具导航站。AI工具列表和GPTs列表通过ChatGPT每天自动更新。\n\nSearch\n\n![Image 2](https://www.toolify.ai/3.3.2/img/card_default.6950039.webp)\n\n i10X \n\n 集成AI平台，500多个AI工具和顶级模型服务于一个订阅。 \n\n![Image 3: i10X](https://cdn-images.toolify.ai/website-logos/20250510/1746849612_55781514_26754.webp)\n\n![Image 4](https://www.toolify.ai/3.3.2/img/card_default.6950039.webp)\n\n Diagrimo \n\n AI 驱动的工具，将想法/文本转换为清晰的图表和信息图。 \n\n![Image 5: Diagrimo](https://cdn-images.toolify.ai/website-logos/20251218/1766029426_22821636_28886.webp)\n\n![Image 6](https://www.toolify.ai/3.3.2/img/card_default.6950039.webp)\n\n Miro \n\n 在线协作白板平台，适用于团队协作和项目管理。 \n\n![Image 7: Miro](https://cdn-images.toolify.ai/website-logos/20250410/1744256650_83434197_1297.webp)\n\n![Image 8](https://www.toolify.ai/3.3.2/img/card_default.6950039.webp)\n\n CrePal \n\n 一体化的 AI 视频代理，帮助你制作 viral AI 视频 \n\n![Image 9: CrePal](https://cdn-images.toolify.ai/website-logos/20250430/1746027988_19222657_26660.webp)\n\n![Image 10](https://www.toolify.ai/3.3.2/img/card_default.6950039.webp)\n\n Rekam AI-Your One-Stop Voice Creation Platform \n\n 全能 AI 声音创作平台，提供文本到语音、声音克隆和语音转文本。 \n\n![Image 11: Rekam AI-Your One-Stop Voice Creation Platform](https://cdn-images.toolify.ai/website-logos/20251220/1766228325_98628321_28910.webp)\n\n![Image 12](https://www.toolify.ai/3.3.2/img/card_default.6950039.webp)\n\n Mailmodo AI \n\n 完整的邮件营销自动化与 AI 代理 \n\n![Image 13: Mailmodo AI](https://cdn-images.toolify.ai/website-logos/20250410/1744260068_32604491_20455.webp)\n\n![Image 14](https://www.toolify.ai/3.3.2/img/card_default.6950039.webp)\n\n Teammates.ai \n\n AI驱动的客户服务、销售和潜在客户生成解决方案。 \n\n![Image 15: Teammates.ai](https://cdn-images.toolify.ai/website-logos/20250411/1744350942_20790031_24407.webp)\n\n![Image 16](https://www.toolify.ai/3.3.2/img/card_default.6950039.webp)\n\n Gobii \n\n 雇佣自动化您的网络工作流程的人工智能员工 — 基于一个全天候运行的生产级平台，无需维护烦恼。 \n\n![Image 17: Gobii](https://cdn-images.toolify.ai/website-logos/20251024/1761269230_98022090_28280.webp)\n\n![Image 18](https://www.toolify.ai/3.3.2/img/card_default.6950039.webp)\n\n ace.me \n\n 你全新的个人网站、电子邮件地址和云存储。简单、快速、安全。 \n\n![Image 19: ace.me](https://cdn-images.toolify.ai/website-logos/20251230/1767085995_34650724_28978.webp)\n\n![Image 20](https://www.toolify.ai/3.3.2/img/card_default.6950039.webp)\n\n Runable \n\n Runable 是一个通用的人工智能代理，可以执行任何任务，从构建网页应用、幻灯片、报告和文档到生成图像、视频和播客，全都在一个平台上。它不仅仅是创建，还能够连接。Runable 与您最喜欢的数千个应用程序集成，您只需告诉它为您完成工作即可。 \n\n![Image 21: Runable](https://cdn-images.toolify.ai/website-logos/20251110/1762768145_57049250_27860.png)\n\n![Image 22](https://www.toolify.ai/3.3.2/img/card_default.6950039.webp)\n\n Kumoo \n\n 专业AI肖像修图 \n\n![Image 23: Kumoo](https://cdn-images.toolify.ai/website-logos/20251018/1760786896_35801499_28223.webp)\n\n![Image 24](https://www.toolify.ai/3.3.2/img/card_default.6950039.webp)\n\n Tripo AI \n\n 基于 AI 的 3D 模型生成器，支持从图像和文本生成 3D 模型。 \n\n![Image 25: Tripo AI](https://cdn-images.toolify.ai/website-logos/20250410/1744267936_15939468_8573.webp)\n\n![Image 26](https://www.toolify.ai/3.3.2/img/card_default.6950039.webp)\n\n WUI.AI \n\n 能够根据你的创意创作角色一致的长视频的 AI 导演。 \n\n![Image 27: WUI.AI](https://cdn-images.toolify.ai/website-logos/20250411/1744363286_22609022_21441.webp)\n\n![Image 28](https://www.toolify.ai/3.3.2/img/card_default.6950039.webp)\n\n Sup AI \n\n Sup AI是世界上最准确的AI编排平台，结合了9种前沿LLMs和专有合成技术，为关键任务决策提供无幻觉的、可验证的响应。 \n\n![Image 29: Sup AI](https://cdn-images.toolify.ai/website-logos/20251206/1765025979_85442179_28783.webp)\n\n![Image 30](https://www.toolify.ai/3.3.2/img/card_default.6950039.webp)\n\n Elser AI \n\n 用于一致性动漫视频的全能AI工作室 \n\n![Image 31: Elser AI](https://cdn-images.toolify.ai/website-logos/20251217/1765966281_88815336_28877.webp)\n\n![Image 32](https://www.toolify.ai/3.3.2/img/card_default.6950039.webp)\n\n Mexty \n\n 基于人工智能的工具，用于创建个性化、互动的在线学习内容。 \n\n![Image 33: Mexty](https://cdn-images.toolify.ai/website-logos/20250723/1753236931_94365356_27441.webp)\n\n[![Image 34](https://www.toolify.ai/3.3.2/img/letter-calendar-index.ff4bd9c.png) 写下关于AI的未来预测 你的预测将直接寄往未来。](https://www.toolify.ai/zh/letters)\n\n今天\n\n[最新AI](https://www.toolify.ai/zh/new)[最多保存](https://www.toolify.ai/zh/most-saved)[最多人使用](https://www.toolify.ai/zh/most-used)[浏览器插件](https://www.toolify.ai/zh/browser-extension)[Apps](https://www.toolify.ai/zh/apps)[Discord of AI](https://www.toolify.ai/zh/discord)\n\n![Image 35](https://www.toolify.ai/3.3.2/img/card_default.6950039.webp)\n\n EverMemOS \n\n Sponsor \n\n Free \n\n 无限记忆。持久身份。演进智能。 EverMemOS 由 EverMind 提供支持，现已在全新云平台开启 Beta 测试。2026 记忆创世纪竞赛也随之正式启动。 \n\n![Image 36: EverMemOS](https://cdn-images.toolify.ai/website-logos/20260309/1773044586_87597902_28639.webp)\n\n[#AI开发者工具](https://www.toolify.ai/zh/category/ai-developer-tools)[#AI智能体](https://www.toolify.ai/zh/category/ai-agent)[#开源AI模型](https://www.toolify.ai/zh/category/open-source-ai-models)[#AI模型](https://www.toolify.ai/zh/category/ai-models)\n\n[![Image 37](https://www.toolify.ai/3.3.2/img/card_default.6950039.webp) VeoNano 利用 Veo 和 Nano Banana 进行高质量视频、图像和音频生成的电影级 AI 工作室。 ![Image 38: VeoNano](https://cdn-images.toolify.ai/website-logos/20260321/1774090968_51570853_29724.webp)](https://www.toolify.ai/zh/tool/veonano)\n\n[#AI